title: Dündarlı, Şehitkamil
content:
Dündarlı is a neighbourhood in the municipality and district of Şehitkamil, Gaziantep Province, Turkey.[1] Its population is 307 (2022).[2] The village is inhabited by Turkmens of the Qiziq tribe, but was formed by Ayrums.[3]
